                <note rend="inline" type="source">358.116 M 82/28a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Sweden</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Morris</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-04-02T17:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 2, 1921—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>17. Department informed Mormon missionaries who are American citizens being
                    forced out of Sweden by authorities and obliged abandon their missionary work
                    and valuable property. Department is unaware of reasons for this action. Ask
                    that nothing drastic be done until matter can be fully investigated. Reply by
                    telegraph.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
